item.title: RAR. files
item.dc:creator: @eijsvogel eijsvogel
item.description:
@eijsvogel wrote:

[quote=“Kyle11594, post:2, topic:169455”]If you have Win.Rar
open your server file.
then right click on any file.
Click select all.
then hit extract to… at the top.
extract it to your My Documents.
then open it up in there…
That will let you log onto your server by yourself. But nobody else can get on it at that point. For information on getting your server open to the public personal message me.[/quote]

Ye i know no other people can connect, but its more that i can play it all alone, so i can figure out how to do things and perhaps later use it

but because i dont got win.RAR, and im not able to get it (im not admin, my dad is, and he is gone for a month)

if possible, can someone ZIP it for me? http://rapidshare.com/files/80142413/Client.rar.html

item.title: RAR. files
item.dc:creator: @Kyle11594 Kyle11594
item.description:
@Kyle11594 wrote:

If you have Win.Rar
open your server file.
then right click on any file.
Click select all.
then hit extract to… at the top.
extract it to your My Documents.
then open it up in there…
That will let you log onto your server by yourself. But nobody else can get on it at that point. For information on getting your server open to the public personal message me.
